{"tid":1973520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★心臟副作用致11患者死　巴西緊急終止氯喹實驗","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T09:18:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a992830f7d47a2257035af3e8a2873d3682b25c","tid":1973520,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）肆虐全球，美國總統特朗普大力吹捧抗瘧疾藥物羥氯喹（Hydroxychloroquine）及氯喹（Chloroquine）有療效。不過有研究顯示，高劑量使用這類藥物，可能會帶來心律不整等致命的副作用。<br />\n<br />\n最近巴西的一個小型臨床實驗，就因11名患者連續6日使用高劑量氯喹後喪命，導致實驗緊急終止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/461153/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BF%83%E8%87%9F%E5%89%AF%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E8%87%B411%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%AD%BB-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E6%B0%AF%E5%96%B9%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F461153%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2587%259F%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%2587%25B411%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%25B0%25AF%25E5%2596%25B9%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=06c8cc88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/461153/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BF%83%E8%87%9F%E5%89%AF%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E8%87%B411%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%AD%BB-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E6%B0%AF%E5%96%B9%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97</a>"},{"pid":"c1094e2a5b3def0a5c8d77a22647e82503725069","tid":1973520,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" cla